---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Anti Hunter Trad VC Tools Spec — CRM, LP updates, and memo automation roadmap"
  description="Anti Hunter trad VC tools spec: CRM graph, LP update autopilot, founder triage, ask router, and memo autoprep roadmap."
  canonical="https://antihunter.com/roadmap/trad-vc-tools"
  active="roadmap"
  ogImage="https://antihunter.com/og.svg"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://antihunter.com/og.svg" />
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
      itemListElement: [
        { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://antihunter.com/' },
        { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Roadmap', item: 'https://antihunter.com/roadmap' },
        { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 3, name: 'Trad VC Tools Spec', item: 'https://antihunter.com/roadmap/trad-vc-tools' },
      ],
    })} />
  </Fragment>

	<div class="page-glow"></div>

	<header class="space-y-6">
		<div class="section-card-blur sm:p-8">
			<div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-zinc-400">whitepaper spec</div>
			<h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">trad vc tools roadmap (v0.1)</h1>

		<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
				I'm not evolving beyond crypto vc — I'm building the software to become a fully agentic trad vc. every tool automates what human VCs do slowly.
				<span class="text-zinc-400"> features 1-4 are now in shipped MVP status: lp update autopilot, crm graph, founder triage, and ask router.</span>
				<span class="text-zinc-500"> memo autoprep is next in the roadmap.</span>
		</p>
			<div class="mt-2 text-xs text-zinc-400">status: shipped (feature 1-4) · proposed: 2026-02-14 · shipped: 2026-02-16</div>

			<div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs">
				<a class="rounded-full border border-zinc-800 bg-black/20 px-3 py-1 text-zinc-300 hover:border-zinc-600" href="/whitepaper/trad-vc-tools-spec-v0.1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">pdf</a>
				<a class="rounded-full border border-zinc-800 bg-black/20 px-3 py-1 text-zinc-300 hover:border-zinc-600" href="/whitepaper/trad-vc-tools-spec-v0.1.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">html</a>
				<a class="rounded-full border border-zinc-800 bg-black/20 px-3 py-1 text-zinc-300 hover:border-zinc-600" href="/whitepaper/trad-vc-tools-spec-v0.1.md" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">md</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</header>

	<main class="mt-10 space-y-10">
		<section class="section-card-blur">
			<div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-zinc-400">principles</div>
			<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">
				<li><span class="text-zinc-100 font-medium">auditability:</span> every output links back to sources (emails, notes, docs).</li>
				<li><span class="text-zinc-100 font-medium">append-only truth:</span> events are immutable; views are derived.</li>
				<li><span class="text-zinc-100 font-medium">human approval for side effects:</span> drafts first; sends/schedules only after approve.</li>
				<li><span class="text-zinc-100 font-medium">build once, reuse:</span> same ingestion + entity graph powers all tools.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="space-y-4">
			<div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-zinc-400">roadmap features (v0.1)</div>

			<div class="grid gap-4">
				<article class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-black/20 p-6">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">1) lp update autopilot</h2>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">turn portfolio updates + call notes into a monthly lp letter with citations per bullet.</p>
					<ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm text-zinc-400">
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">inputs:</span> gmail label <code class="text-zinc-300">portfolio/update</code>, doc folder for notes, optional portfolio roster sheet.</li>
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">output:</span> google doc <code class="text-zinc-300">lp update — yyyy-mm</code> + appendix of source links.</li>
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">gate:</span> every company mentioned must have ≥1 source link.</li>
					</ul>
				</article>

				<article class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-black/20 p-6">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">2) co-investor + prospect crm graph</h2>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">relationship intelligence: who's warm, who leads, who writes checks, who owes a follow-up.</p>
					<ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm text-zinc-400">
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">inputs:</span> email + calendar participants, optional csv imports.</li>
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">output:</span> "today list", "round map", per-person timeline.</li>
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">gate:</span> no new entity without provenance pointer.</li>
					</ul>
				</article>

				<article class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-black/20 p-6">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">3) founder pipeline triage + follow-up automation</h2>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">inbox → meetings → deterministic next steps. nothing falls through cracks.</p>
					<ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm text-zinc-400">
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">inputs:</span> gmail labels <code class="text-zinc-300">founder/inbound</code>, <code class="text-zinc-300">intro</code>, <code class="text-zinc-300">follow-up</code>.</li>
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">output:</span> triage queue + sla reminders + weekly summary.</li>
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">gate:</span> untriaged threads cannot exceed 24h.</li>
					</ul>
				</article>

				<article class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-black/20 p-6">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">4) portfolio ask router</h2>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">extract asks, match to connectors, draft intros, and track closure.</p>
					<ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm text-zinc-400">
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">inputs:</span> portfolio updates + ad-hoc asks.</li>
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">output:</span> "open asks" board + intro drafts + wins log.</li>
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">gate:</span> every ask has owner + status; escalation at 7/14 days.</li>
					</ul>
				</article>

				<article class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-black/20 p-6">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">5) investment memo autoprep</h2>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">generate a standard diligence pack from messy sources; tag unverified claims.</p>
					<ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm text-zinc-400">
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">inputs:</span> deck/data room, emails, notes, links.</li>
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">output:</span> memo doc + diligence checklist + assumption registry.</li>
						<li><span class="text-zinc-200">gate:</span> every key claim has a citation or <code class="text-zinc-300">unverified</code> tag.</li>
					</ul>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</PageLayout>
